{"operationName":"AllFundsByAddress","variables":{"address":"0x7e4abd63a7c8314cc28d388303472353d884f292"},"query":"query AllFundsByAddress($address: String!) {
  allFundsByInvestor(investorAddress: $address) {
    fundAddress
    fundName
    investorBalance
    adjustedTokenPrice
    investmentValue
    returnOnInvestment
    roiUsd
    blockchainCode
    managerAddress
    managerName
    createdAt
    badges {
      name
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
  allFundsByManager(managerAddress: $address) {
    address
    name
    totalValue
    managerFeeNumerator
    adjustedTokenPrice
    blockchainCode
    score
    managerAddress
    blockTime
    __typename
  }
  allFundsByTrader(traderAddress: $address) {
    address
    name
    totalValue
    managerFeeNumerator
    adjustedTokenPrice
    blockchainCode
    score
    managerAddress
    blockTime
    __typename
  }
}"}

requests.postData:
{"operationName":"AllFundsByAddress","variables":{"address":"0x7e4abd63a7c8314cc28d388303472353d884f292"},"query":"query AllFundsByAddress($address: String!) {
  allFundsByInvestor(investorAddress: $address) {
    fundAddress
    fundName
    investorBalance
    adjustedTokenPrice
    investmentValue
    returnOnInvestment
    roiUsd
    blockchainCode
    managerAddress
    managerName
    createdAt
    badges {
      name
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
  allFundsByManager(managerAddress: $address) {
    address
    name
    totalValue
    managerFeeNumerator
    adjustedTokenPrice
    blockchainCode
    score
    managerAddress
    blockTime
    __typename
  }
  allFundsByTrader(traderAddress: $address) {
    address
    name
    totalValue
    managerFeeNumerator
    adjustedTokenPrice
    blockchainCode
    score
    managerAddress
    blockTime
    __typename
  }
}"}
